# VisibilityType

Specifies if a template is available on a user (Personal) or a company (Company) level

**Properties**

| Name     | Type | Required | Description |
| :------- | :--- | :------- | :---------- |
| COMPANY  | str  | ✅       | "Company"   |
| PERSONAL | str  | ✅       | "Personal"  |
